nario set up displays&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    3 Economic display mats&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    1 Events table card&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    100 color, die-cut two-sided 1/2&amp;quot; square pieces&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    40 color, die-cut 5/8&amp;quot; square pieces&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    90 color, die-cut 1/2&amp;quot; round pieces&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    56 color, die-cut 5/8&amp;quot; round pieces&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    40 Event cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Design: Gary W. Graber&amp;#10;Additional Design and Development: Alan Emrich with Carl Paradis&amp;#10;Graphics: Alan Emrich&amp;#10;Map: Tim Allen&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
